e.	Require the OIC-Municipal Accountant to ensure that all PPEs subject for    depreciation have been provided with depreciation expense and to prepare for Local Road Network a lapsing schedule for the computation of the depreciation for all road networks and its component pursuant to Section 7 of COA Circular No. 2015-008 dated November 23, 2015; and

f.	Oblige the Inventory Committee to submit to the Audit Team the RPCPPE duly reconciled with the accounting and property records, not later than the 10th day of January of the following year.

